        "setup": "Create a webhook with the [Create a webhook](https://developers.vendr.com/api/webhooks-api#create-a-webhook) endpoint. Vendr says each delivery is signed with `x-vendr-webhook-signature` using HMAC SHA-256 and `your auto-generated webhook secret`; the example notes this secret is \"Returned once from the create webhook endpoint; store securely\". Save that returned secret and use it to verify incoming webhook deliveries.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
